{"tid":362102,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"各位點睇揾水抱","createTime":"2017-08-16T16:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T14:04:13.000Z","uid":137552,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"335305648b90551a3aa94125ce3a9a3b565ee677","tid":362102,"uid":137552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:01:46.000Z","msg":"鐘意咗一個女仔兩年，但係佢一直都冇咩表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係又會有暗示話考完Dse先諗呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我就感受到我地之間有距離感(例如一日覆兩次wts，有時甚至失蹤。但係見到佢係online緊)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我都慢慢心淡，甚至冇再揾佢。重點來啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我身邊就一直有一個女仔，佢都暗示過對我有好感，不過我就因為鐘意緊第二個，所以當時就捥拒咗佢。但係依加我覺得佢慢慢取代緊第一個女仔，我心入面好困惑。我到底係對佢有好感，定係只係當佢水抱來填補我心入面第一個女仔嘅位置。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有冇類似情況可以分享下，教下我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：第一次開post勿問候伯母"},{"pid":"ae986f65d91e5fc5db05d6d514a936ffc4e50036","tid":362102,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"水抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dc83536fda2ab9796199a8f6392138ded9e8e6","tid":362102,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:03:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"880c92d1d581f145b20b85d137ee3f033f7a397d","tid":362102,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"情傷好痛㗎 愛情呢樣嘢你估真係咁好玩呀？"},{"pid":"5eeb261f2ff51d4b4b530d8fb830b8af000e1c39","tid":362102,"uid":90178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"屌穿你個糸"},{"pid":"9f39b1ae01c6ed7399bf6f25a4a17bdef3a9d75b","tid":362102,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"dse都未考就咪諗